reviews: I love these sunglasses. They are the perfect fit and size for people who like a slightly oversized aviator. The frames are super sturdy, expensive quality for a fraction of the price. The reason for 4 stars is that they did not come with a case. In fact, there wasn’t even a box. My glasses arrived in just a plastic zip bag inside of the amazon bubble bag. It could have easily been squashed and broken during shipping. I was very lucky mine came pristine despite the awful packaging. That would be the only thing to be wary of when purchasing.
